data.description: Welcome home to this delightful 3-bedroom, 1 bathroom bungalow nestled in a prime location just minutes away from Southfield Freeway, I 94, and "The Hill" shopping area.  Downstairs, a partially finished basement presents endless possibilities—a versatile area ideal for a home office, recreation room, or additional storage, tailored to suit your needs.  The furnace and central air are less than a year old.   The fenced in back yard is perfect for outdoor gatherings and pets. The one-car garage opens to the alley.   Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming bungalow your new home sweet home! Schedule a showing today!
